Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.35,0:00:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Beloved doctor and Susan, thank you for\Nletting us say goodbye to you by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,expressing a gratitude from our hearts.\NI want to begin with a tribute to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.64,0:00:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,from someone who couldn't be here today\Nbut who loves you very much. Michael
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Beckwith.\NMichael Beckwith is the founder of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Agape International Spiritual Center.\NHere is his tribute to you. It is my
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.96,0:00:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,joy, David, to speak directly to you on\Nthis extraordinary occasion of your last
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,public appearance.\NWhile you may think that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,disappearing from the public eye, the\Nenergy frequency of your love,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,compassion, and wisdom remains in every\Nheart you have touched throughout these
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:01:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,many years. And certainly that includes\Nmy own and that of my spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,community.\NYou are a cosmic blessing on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.28,0:01:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a beneficial presence whose imprint is\Ndeep and eternal. I love you, brother. I
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,love you.\N>> God bless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.15,0:01:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,>> That was from Michael.\N>> God bless Michael Beckwith. God bless
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you, brother.\NAnd uh now we have a ceremonial tribute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,from South Korea.\N>> They're going to do a special
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.75,0:01:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> What? Honey,\N>> they're doing a special
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.84,0:01:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh, boy.\NThat's terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.\N>> Ain't that something?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much. I'm greatly honored.\N>> Oh, that was beautiful. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I'm greatly honored.\N>> Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you ladies.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.48,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they from Korea?\NThank you ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the Buddha called Ananda and said\Nsaid to him, "It may be Ananda that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,after my passing away, you might think\Ngone is the utterance of our master. We
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,have no master anymore." But you should\Nnot think so, Ananda, for the doctrine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and discipline which I've taught you and\Nprescribed to you will be your master
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,after my death. Now, oh monks, I exhort\Nyou, exhort you, all compounded things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are subject to decay. Work for your\Nsalvation with honestness. These were
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.40,0:04:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the Buddha's last words.\NBut for the presence of saints on earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the world would burn to death.\NWe pray for you. So long as we live, we
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:05:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,live in your remembrance and on our\Ndeath be blessed with your vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.\NGod bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful.\NThis is Ganes Water from India.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ganjes water from India.\N>> Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you.\NI don't want to lose this this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,water from the Ganges River.\N>> As everybody knows, the Ganges River is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,blessed and calibrates extremely high.\NWhat does it calibrate at? I forget. 700
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,over 500, 600, 700. It calibrates at\N700. The Ganges River calibrates at 700
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.52,0:06:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,because of the sacredness of its\Ndedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.08,0:06:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you\N>> on behalf of uh all the followers of uh
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. David Hawkins teachings from India.\NDr. Hawkins teachings have touched the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,beginners in the spirituality starting\Nfrom the beginners in the spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.40,0:06:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,up to the scholars who spend years in\Nstudying the scriptures in Sanskrit and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.31,0:06:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,then they become very exponents when we\Nhave distributed the books of Dr.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.12,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawkins to the beginners they felt that\Nit has cleared many of their spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,doubts and it has inspired them touched\Nthem and transformed them. Equally so
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,when these books have been given to the\Nscholars who had spent years in the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,research in spirituality they also felt\Nthat it has stretched and transformed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.84,0:07:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,them and whatever they have learned all\Nthese years in their spiritual research
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they could find the same teachings in\NDr. David Hawkins books and they felt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,touched and transformed. What we have\Ndone is we have integrated Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,teachings along with the Indian\Nscriptures and then we have spread this
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.56,0:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,message to many youngsters and adults\Nand old people alike and all of them
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,have been uplifted and greatly benefited\Nby Dr. Hawkins teachings which makes the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,scriptural understanding much more\Nsimple much more easier and more clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So on behalf of all the followers I\Noffer humble prostrations and respects
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:08:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,to Dr. Dr. David Hawkins for making a\Ngreat difference in all of our lives and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,may your teachings be with us forever\Nbecause we have already integrated them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,into our regular satssung and spiritual\Ndiscourses and workshops and seminars
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and so on and so forth. So we continue\Nto feel your presence and we continue to
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,feel your blessings. Har\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you. God bless you.\NGod bless you. God bless you. God bless
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you. God bless you.\N>> God bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The water from the Ganges,\Nas everyone here knows,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates extremely high.\NCalibrates at 700.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,700.\NThat's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible. Here's March Brit. March\NBrits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> It is such a great honor to be here with\Nyou today, Dr. David Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. Marge Britt.\NI'm the minister, senior minister of
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,unity in Tustin, California, where you\Ncame to speak at our center uh in 2003.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You have been one of the most profound\Nspiritual teachers of my entire life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and your teachings from the moment that\NI found them have impacted the teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that I do in unity and beyond.\NAs the vice president of our
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.60,0:10:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,international seminary,\NI'm also aware of the impact that you've
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.76,0:10:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,had worldwide.\NOne of my fondest memories of you is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.27,0:10:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when you came to Unity Village to meet\Nwith students and with the hierarchy of
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Unity School of Christianity.\NWe were between meetings going from
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,meeting with the students to a meeting\Nwith the hierarchy, walking quickly to
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.07,0:10:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,get to the next meeting, and suddenly\Nyou disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone looked around to try to find\Nyou and we located you a few moments
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,later in the rose garden smelling the\Nroses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You have always brought beauty and joy.\NYour energy, your consciousness, your
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,vibration was a match for unity and is a\Nmatch for new thought and is a match for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Christianity.\NAnd
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot thank you enough for what you\Nhave given in the world. how you have
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,made the teachings of Jesus and other\Nmaster teachers literally come alive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.95,0:11:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,through your very being and your very\Nconsciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will be eternally grateful for you\Nand for Susan who said to you, you must
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,write and you must teach.\N>> Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yes.\NLet me see you as I remember who you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,are.\N>> Oh, there you are. Yes, I see you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:12:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,honey. Thank you.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.32,0:12:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me.\NCall the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\N>> Hi, Dr. Hawkins and Susan. Um, I'm from
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,South Africa. We have a few students\Nfrom South Africa. Will you please stand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,up,\N>> South Africa, there's more students back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,at home and your work is spreading\Nslowly but surely. And I just want to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you from the bottom of my heart\Nfor everything that you've given us and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,all of mankind. Thank you very much.\NThank you, Lord. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lord. Amen.\N>> Hi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from uh the Channel Islands.\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,>> In the United Kingdom.\N>> He's from where?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Channel Islands.\N>> The Channel Islands in the United
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Kingdom.\N>> Oh, the Channel Islands. Yes. Yes. And
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,um on behalf of the United Kingdom um\Nwould all the students from the United
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.88,0:13:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Kingdom like to stand up.\N>> What do they say here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd like to say thank you and your work\Nwill live on in our hearts and it is a
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,pleasure to live your truth.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless.\NHello Dr. Hawkins. Hello Susan. We are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from Germany and also in behalf\Nof all the Germans Dr. Hawkins students
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and the rest of the European students we\Nlike to say thank you very much for all
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.20,0:14:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you have done for us. You have changed\Nour life and we are grateful beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,words. Maybe all the European students\Nlike to stand up now and thank our
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher\NGuten Don.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you. Thank you.\NI work in the medical field and I've had
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the opportunity to see how much these\Nideas can help patients who are working
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,on different issues.\NAnd there's so many ways but of of them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,all I think the main help they've got is\Nto be introduced to the idea that uh the
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,ego comes from the animal level as so\Nmany are locked in guilt. self-hatred
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and judgment.\NAnd when it's explained to them that the
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,ego comes from the animal, that it's a\Nvery good animal, it's very good at what
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it does,\Nthere's no need to hate it or to destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,it, but to understand it and just\Ndisengage from it has been most helpful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,probably of all that I've done with them\Nover time. And also, they can make
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,friends with their little animal.\NAnd I tell him that Dr. Hawkins loves
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to his little teddy bear.\NAnd he'll say to it, "They cut you off
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,in traffic. Of course, they should be\Npunished."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it softens it for them so much.\NSometimes they go on and uh buy books
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and DVDs to study further. And then I\Nknow they're going to learn in a hundred
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,different ways that all healing is\Npossible for one reason only, the love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,of God. So on their behalf and mine too,\NDr. Hawkins, thank you so much for your
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,life's work and for all you've given us.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N>> Hi, Dr. Hawkins. Hello everyone. And I
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,was asked to um speak briefly on what I\Nwitness as a psychotherapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought I'd ask all\Npsychotherapists to please stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.75,0:16:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Now if uh all psychotherapy patients can\Nplease stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's so many things to say,\Nbut um
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.48,0:16:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,uh as a therapist, Dr. Hawkins, uh you\Ngive such reverence and respect for the
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,full spectrum of physical, mental,\Nspiritual. So, I can say as a therapist,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.88,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've uh so many patients have benefit\Nfrom simply seeing a psychiatrist and
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,getting on medication. And many more\Nhave benefited from availing themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.24,0:17:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of 12 steps\Nwork and spiritual work. Um, one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd just like to add, uh, is that Dr.\NHawkins often says, of course, it's not
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,where you are as a clinician, it's where\Nthey are. And, uh, I found your work
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,profound in helping me to meet, uh,\Nclients where they are. And, uh, really
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the simple things using humor. I've I've\Nbasically pretended like every joke
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you've ever said is mine.\NAnd I crack your jokes in sessions all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the time. And um and uh you also say Dr.\NHawkins that um deep down what we all
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,want is a recognition of what we truly\Nare. And I feel like as a therapist I
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,just I'm a witness to the truth of\Ntruth. And um and that love really does
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,heal and that we just really need to\Nstep back and allow uh love to do what
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.84,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,love does. So thank you Dr. Hawkins.\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.55,0:18:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Hi, Dr. Hawkins. Um, we're here\Nrepresenting all the families who are
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,raising children and doing the work. I\Nwant to thank you. And one teaching who
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that's been very beneficial to me is\Nknowing that all that I have to do is be
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the very best wife that I can be and be\Nthe very best mother that I can be and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that is uplifting mankind. Thank you.\NThank you for the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:19:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And so parenting with Dr. Hawkins work\Nhas meant for us that um the kids never
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,ask us to go on any vacation\Nbut instead to go to the Buddha relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um it has also meant that they always\Nremind us to forgive everybody whenever
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,they get in trouble.\NAnd um
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.44,0:19:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,uh more than anything it has taught us\Nto practice unconditional lovingness and
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to see divinity in everything, not just\Non the isolated mountaintop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins said one time that there's\Nno greater gift to give to mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,than to perfect this state.\NAnd the greatest gift we have received
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.79,0:19:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is to be allowed to witness that.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.64,0:20:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Namaste Dr. Hawkins, Susan, and everyone\Nat Veritas Pub.
