Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.96,0:39:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.\N>> Sit back and rest your bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.52,0:39:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Dr. Hark and Susan.\Nuh he who dwells in the protection of
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.04,0:39:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the most high shall abide under the\Nshadow of the almighty. Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.72,0:39:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,beloved teachers.\N>> Dr. Hawkins, um thank you Susan. Thank
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.11,0:39:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you. uh your your work facilitated a\Nprofound spiritual experience inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:40:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and um from that I was able to stop\Ndrinking using get into a program and um
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.04,0:40:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,today I'm not the most loving person but\Num I'm going that way
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.32,0:40:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a God in my\NYeah. and um what you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.88,0:40:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,in in\Nas far as God goes, you know, I get I
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.83,0:40:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,get to see and feel him in my life and\Nand um and that's a result of everything
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.44,0:40:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,that you've given to me and I'm\Neternally grateful. Thank you. Thank
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.68,0:40:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you.\NDoc, at age 18, I was kicked out of my
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.35,0:40:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,house. I have five siblings and mom and\Ndad still alive. I spent several decades
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.83,0:41:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,um trying to overcome resentments and\Nanger and with some progress until, you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.40,0:41:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,know, the next thing would happen and\NI'd get kicked in the gut. And
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.76,0:41:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when I found your work, the map and and\Nyour lectures, it became very obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.52,0:41:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that everyone's just doing the best that\Nthey can. And
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.88,0:41:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the transformation in my family has just\Nbeen phenomenal. I'm have the best
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.35,0:41:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship with my mom and dad that\NI've ever had um in weekly communication
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.96,0:41:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or more and with my siblings and it's\Nall gone just incredibly well and I know
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.48,0:41:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak for many here that you're a\Nfather figure to me and uh have taught
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.88,0:41:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,me a lot about strength and courage and\Ntenderness and thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.04,0:42:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, there are no words worthy\Nof expression of what I found within
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.16,0:42:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,through your teachings.\N>> Doc and Susan,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.11,0:42:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,God, thank you so much. Um,\NI spent 10 years of my life in
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.28,0:42:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,addiction. over five years of that time\Nshooting heroin in and out of jails,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.04,0:42:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,living on the street.\NBy the mercy of the Lord, I was exposed
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.68,0:42:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to your teachings in rehab\Na few years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.72,0:42:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I now live a sober life full of joy. You\Nbrought me to Christ. You brought me to
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.24,0:42:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Krishna. You brought me to the rooms of\Nrecovery and the steps of recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.72,0:42:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wake up in the morning grateful to be\Nalive. I thought I was condemned to the
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.24,0:42:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,life I was living for the rest of my\Nlife. And I wake up a free man by your
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.88,0:43:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,grace. By your grace. And\NGod, you saved my life. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.83,0:43:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I want to thank you for your\Nteachings as they uh uh firstly they got
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.35,0:43:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,me out of atheism uh using logic and\Nreason
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.40,0:43:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh also for about uh 25 years um I\Nhad uh a lot of panic and fear uh which
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.31,0:43:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,manifest itself in uh irrital bowel\Nsyndrome and um using your techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.16,0:43:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that you uh describe in u um handling\Nmajor life crisis uh uh in about five
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.96,0:43:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes I was able to handle that fear\Nand energy and just like you state just
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.40,0:44:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,look straight ahead surrender to God and\Njust ignore the energies and they they
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.00,0:44:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,dissipated and in about 5 years I was\Nable to transcend something uh that had
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.40,0:44:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,really uh ruled my life for well 25\Nyears. So, uh thank you so much for
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.28,0:44:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,everything. Um thank you so much.\NDear Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.72,0:44:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and dear Dr. Hawkins,\NI thank both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.00,0:44:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,from the depth of my heart\Nand my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.64,0:44:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,for what I have given and what I have\Ngained from you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.83,0:44:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is incredible. My life has changed so\Nmuch.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.83,0:44:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's indescribable.\NI thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.44,0:45:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And I love you both. And I love all of\Nyou, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.88,0:45:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I'm an alcoholic and a heroin addict\Nand a crackhead. And my name is
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.76,0:45:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Danielle. And I heard one of your\Nrecordings eight years ago. And um, your
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.07,0:45:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness communicated with mine.\Nand I received the gift of inspiration
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.83,0:45:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I couldn't stop drinking and I\Ncouldn't stop using but I also couldn't
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.96,0:45:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,stop listening and I couldn't stop\Nreading
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.64,0:45:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I came and I saw you for the\Nfirst time years later and when I left I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.64,0:45:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,left with the gift gift of desperation\NI don't think how I used to think. I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.11,0:45:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,don't feel how I used to feel and I\Ndon't act how I used to act. And I know
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.88,0:45:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that you gave me those two gifts and God\Ndid the rest. And today I love and I
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.40,0:46:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,give and I tell people about the\Nteachings. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.76,0:46:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Offens Susan. uh when I when I first\Ncame to your lecture uh in 2005, you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.04,0:46:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,told me that uh I was seeking a teacher,\Na spiritual teacher and you told me that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.72,0:46:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,uh what I seek I will find and I\Ngrateful to God's grace that uh he's
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.44,0:46:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,brought Dr. Hawkins to me as a spiritual\Nteacher. I don't think I could have
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.92,0:46:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,continued uh this journey, this\Nspiritual journey without uh Dr. Hawkins
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.16,0:46:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,as a teacher and and his inspiration and\Nhis uh
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.00,0:46:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,guidance, his divine guidance and the uh\Nthe incredible energy uh the the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.80,0:46:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of the I guess the divine presence that\Nemanates it always puts me into uh
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.72,0:47:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway uh\Nthere like my life's been changed
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.83,0:47:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,through his teachings. I' I've been\Nfollowing a spiritual path most of my
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.96,0:47:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,life and I was very fortunate to have\Ngood teachers along the way and and I
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.28,0:47:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,feel that Dr. Hawkins is my last and\Nfinal teacher and I will follow his
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.83,0:47:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,teachings\Nforever. Thank you Dr. Hawkins. Thank
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.96,0:47:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you Susan.\NWe have to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.96,0:47:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings Dr. Hawkins from New Zealand.\NUm I'm not a poet, but the last few
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.35,0:47:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,days, um quite a few lines have been\Nrunning around in my head, so I put them
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.92,0:47:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,on paper, not knowing that this\Nopportunity was going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.16,0:47:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflections on the impact of the\Nwritings of Dr. David R. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.00,0:47:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The clarion call rises. The challenge\Nmade in every book. Straight and narrow
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.04,0:48:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is the path. Waste of no time. But dear\Nfriends, the path has been so brightly
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.88,0:48:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,lit by the divine words within these\Nworks of devotional non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.80,0:48:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For this life, the straight and narrow\Npath rises effortlessly to meet every
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.59,0:48:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,step forward, to comfort every stalled\Nstep, and to guide the gathering pace of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.31,0:48:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,growing consciousness.\NOutwardly,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.24,0:48:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a newly found constant smile echoes the\Nflow of growing love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.00,0:48:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Inwardly\Npeace and joy endure despite the artful
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.96,0:48:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,challenges of the ego.\NUnderstanding shifts to knowing and
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.16,0:48:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,being.\NHow pure, how true the experiences of
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.24,0:48:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,devotional non-duality. Gloria in\Nexcelsius deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.80,0:49:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Thank you.\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.59,0:49:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband and I give thanks for you\Nevery night in our prayers, but I feel
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.28,0:49:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,compelled to express my gratitude\Ntowards you in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.55,0:49:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It is challenging to find words to\Nexpress how eternally grateful I am for
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.52,0:49:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the both of you and for the work. I know\NI must be blessed with excellent karma
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.16,0:49:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,to have found your teachings so young in\Nlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.00,0:49:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You have shown me how to recontextualize\Nmy entire life and that has made all the
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.40,0:49:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,difference. It hasn't been an easy trip,\Nbut I feel that you have provided me
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.11,0:49:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,with the proper tools to survive on the\Nsometimes treacherous but mostly
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.52,0:49:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,beautiful journey.\NThe tools you have given me include a
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.48,0:49:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,shield that cannot be punctured by\Ndoubt, a helmet full of knowledge to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.40,0:50:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,know who and what to avoid, a compass\Nwhose only direction is truth, shoes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.80,0:50:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,made of courage that only follow the\Nstraight and narrow path, and the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.20,0:50:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,greatest tool of all, love.\NA love that I can't even begin to
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.44,0:50:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,express into words. I thank you with\Nevery ounce of my existence and I love
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.55,0:50:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you both so very much.\N>> That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.59,0:50:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I\Njust
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.07,0:50:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> We wait for everybody in the audience to\Nget a hold of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.88,0:50:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\N>> Do you want to say hello or goodbye or
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.55,0:50:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,>> do you want to say goodbye? Just Do you\Nwant to just say goodbye to the crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.16,0:50:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Yeah.\N>> And then
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.88,0:50:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I give thanks to the Lord God\Nfor the loving presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.44,0:51:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I give thanks to thee, oh Lord, for thy\Nloving presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.55,0:51:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,For that is what you are.\NYou are the loving presence of God
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.04,0:51:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty\Nfor which I am eternally grateful. God
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.83,0:51:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,bless you in the name of the Father, the\NSon, and the Holy Spirit now and
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.04,0:51:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,forever. Amen.\N>> We love you. We love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.44,0:51:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,>> We love you.\NYou
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.59,0:51:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> hear the pipe stuck. You hear the pipes?\N>> They better or I'll kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.28,0:52:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Oh, God bless the pipes.\NWhat are they calibrated at? 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.20,0:52:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?\NWhere are they? They calibrated 500,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.31,0:54:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,right?\NHeat. Heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.11,0:55:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,heat. Hey\NHeat. Heat.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.44,0:56:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Heat.\NHeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.35,0:56:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.\NStay right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.76,0:57:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> What? Just Just stay right there. You'll\Nfine.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.48,0:57:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.35,0:57:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.92,0:58:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.48,0:58:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.96,0:58:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelu\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.16,0:59:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.00,0:59:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.55,0:59:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.96,1:00:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.24,1:00:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.92,1:00:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.83,1:00:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelu.\NMy work has come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.31,1:00:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And with our work, it lives on in each\None of you. So go out to the world and
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.64,1:01:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,spread the word.\NChange people's lives like we have done.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.64,1:01:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You've heard the testimony. You know the\Nresults.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.28,1:01:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> So, it's up to each one of you to change\Nsomeone else's life now that yours has
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.24,1:01:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,been changed.\NThe last 10 years that we have done this
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.59,1:01:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,has been so rewarding to us. And if I\Ncould just pass that along, how
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.40,1:01:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,rewarding this whole change will be for\Nyou to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.88,1:01:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All it takes is just one person\Nto help one person to change one life to
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.88,1:01:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,change one life around.\NWe love you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.68,1:02:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,>> We wish we could continue, but we can't.\N>> You'll be in our hearts forever, and we
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.68,1:02:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,will see your faces in our dreams.\NWe carry all your spirits with us and
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.52,1:02:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,hope we meet again.\N>> Love to you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.28,1:02:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> We love you, Dr. Hawkins.\Nbefore I get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.44,1:03:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,>> It's too hard. It's too hard to talk.\N>> Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.48,1:03:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\N>> Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.72,1:03:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Dr. Hawkins,\Nlove you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.20,1:03:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I\Nam greatly honored by your love.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.24,1:03:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I am greatly honored by your love.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.28,1:03:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I love you now and forever.\NIn the name of my Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.59,1:04:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen\NJesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.92,1:04:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Amen.\N>> Stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.55,1:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Huh?\N>> Stay strong. Don't give up.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.40,1:04:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\N>> Love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.72,1:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.59,1:05:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.48,1:05:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.24,1:05:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Halleluah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.55,1:05:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.64,1:05:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.72,1:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.28,1:06:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.76,1:06:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelu.\NHalleluah.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.76,1:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Halle.
